jfxtras.scene.control.agenda.icalendar.factories

Class RecurrenceFactory<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • jfxtras.scene.control.agenda.icalendar.factories.RecurrenceFactory<R>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultRecurrenceFactory

    public abstract class RecurrenceFactory<R>
extends java.lang.Object

    Abstract factory to create recurrences from VComponents. getStartRange() and getEndRange() must be set before recurrences can be made.
